name: Wikipedia - DarkBlue
description:
Dark Blue Wikipedia. Optimized for reading articles, so some links and clutter have been removed such as the login and community features. Tested on Firefox/Nightly 26.0a1. Let me know what you think.

• UPD 092013 - I'm working towards getting this tested outside of Firefox...a couple days at the most. I'll fix the font definitions for non-Windows clients shortly.

• UPD 092913 - Updated fonts for non-Windows clients and other misc tweaks.

• UPD 093013 - Verified compatibility on Firefox, Chrome and Opera on PC platform. Additional misc tweaks.

• UPD 011914 - Misc tweaks.

• UPD 060614 - Fixed the directional icons for sortable tables. Other misc tweaks.
